title: Hour 2: Witty Orders Code Zed
description:
Mike Schur continues his attempt at being fired by insulting Dan, Stu, and the Shipping Container after delivering his Stat of the Day. Plus, yesterday's Team A vs. Team B drama has spilled over to today as Witty is called out for being a fraud.
